Also add to the imports at the top of traits.rs:
```rust
use crate::chunking_pipeline::FormatRegistry;
use crate::chunking_strategy::SourceFile;
```

NOTE: This is a breaking change. The adapter-git crate will fail to compile until Task 8. That's expected — this is a pre-release clean break per D69.

**Step 3: Verify corvia-kernel compiles**

Run: `cargo check -p corvia-kernel`
Expected: PASS (kernel itself doesn't implement the trait)

Run: `cargo check -p corvia-adapter-git`
Expected: FAIL (expected — adapter still implements old trait)

**Step 4: Commit**

```bash
git add crates/corvia-kernel/src/traits.rs
git commit -m "feat(m3.3): revise IngestionAdapter trait — D69 clean break"
